posts.html:
About

We harness synthesizers among other instruments to explore sound and audio aesthetic. Sonic texture, dynamic rhythm, samples, and exotic melody come together through Dematerialised Identities. We're synthesists chasing comets; explorations of synesthesia and visual atmosphere continue with
Ambient Artstyles.

Professionally, we work with developers to create immersive sonic environments. We contribute audio aesthetics which evoke emotion and atmosphere complementary to your world under construction.

Contact

Chat with us on Discord
For Professional Inquiries: DematerialisedSocieties [at] protonmail.com

Details:

Sound Design, Composition, Arrangement, Programming with:
Foley, Field Recording, Sampling, Sequencing, Environmental Ambience, Creatures, Dialog, Multi-Channel 3-D Spatial Audio, Wwise, and Unity.

Phase 1
Guiding parameters identified; initial production.

- Asset list
- Guiding Composition
- Ambient Atmospheric Soundscape & Sample Palette

Phase 2
Interactive Review.

- Secondary Production
- Second Sound Design
- Initial programming (+)

Phase 3
- Mastering
- Multi-Instrument Arrangement (+)
- Finale Sound Programming (+)

We harness synthesizers among other instruments to explore sound and audio

posts.html:
Upcoming Albums

  • Gravity and Grit and tales of Rocket Science remind us of our place among the stars. A journey which stands on the shoulders of giants and encapsulates the exit velocity of science and human experience.

  • Towards the horizon our eyes are set as we explore the story of the Ghost Ship of 1482. A merchant vessel lost to the blue.

Find our most recent releases on SoundCloud.

posts.html:
Thoughts manifest on digital canvas, transmissions through the datastream.

It has been said that there is much to grok but little to grok from, yet prime material exists everywhere on our way to the Technocore. Consider your mind and your <entwined emotions>. Is the weird a discomfort || a valley of familiarity? Together, we explore experiential understanding bit by bit. Slow your mind and let the journey continue as we conjure visual echoes through digital alchemy.

@ambientartstyles

posts.html:
Merely the sonic manifestation of your Eternal Dreams.

We invite you to join us as we explore sonic environments in the digital frontier. Sometimes the space is pleasant, other times challenging but always the exploration is worth the journey. Unbound, we investigate driving, atmospheric, and curious sound.  

Once you free your mind about music being correct, you can do whatever you want

Dematerialised Identities · Full range
posts.plaintext:
Merely the sonic manifestation of your Eternal Dreams.
[https://youtu.be/W59B6fpyLo0?t=11]

We invite you to join us as we explore sonic environments in the digital
frontier. Sometimes the space is pleasant, other times challenging but always
the exploration is worth the journey. Unbound, we investigate driving,
atmospheric, and curious sound.
